:: From-Behind-Dialogue [nobr]

<<if $sex.role == "Top">>
    <<ref _top 'subjCap'>> <<be _top>> behind <<ref _bottom 'subj'>>, who is on all fours.
<<elseif $sex.role == "Bottom">>
    <<ref _bottom 'subjCap'>> <<be _bottom>> on all fours with <<ref _top 'subj'>> behind <<ref _bottom 'subj'>>.
<</if>>